<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="presence-n">presence <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'prezns/    美 /'prezns/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>出席；到场；存在</strong></h4>
<p>反 absence： </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He hardly seemed to notice my presence.
他似乎没有注意到我的存在。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-the-presence-of-sb-in-sbs-presence">in the presence of sb / in sb’s presence</h3>
<p>1.<strong>当着某人的面：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He apologized to her in the presence of the whole family. 
他当着全家人的面向她道歉。</p></div></div>